<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Leander" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Leander,</orth> the lover of Hero: <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 1, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.120" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 120</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.2.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 2, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.100" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 1, 100</bibl>. Corrupted to <emph>Limander</emph> by the performer of Pyramus in <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.198" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 198</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>